and staying with us.

1012
00:40:19.570 --> 00:40:22.270
We filmed during
really trying times.

1013
00:40:22.370 --> 00:40:25.310
but we pushed through and I
am so thankful for your love

1014
00:40:25.410 --> 00:40:27.311
