1030
00:41:02.455 --> 00:41:03.595
Thank you.

1031
00:41:03.695 --> 00:41:05.875
You guys blew the show up.

1032
00:41:05.975 --> 00:41:08.276
Truly became a word
of mouth success.

1033
00:41:08.376 --> 00:41:10.576
And it's the reason why we
